Ogun State Governor, Dapo Abiodun, has finally sent his 18 – man list of commissioner – nominees to the State House of Assembly for screening and possible confirmation. Daily Trust reports that the appointment comes barely seven months after Abiodun assumed office as the governor of the state.  Abiodun finally nominates commissioners 6 months after 8 weeks after inauguration... 26 govs yet to form cabinet Disquiet in Ogun APC over commissioners’ appointment